{
  "stem": "15017.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I went in and applied.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the man said to me, what do you know about Selmer instruments?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, first of all, I'm a professional musician.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Next, I used to sell Selmer instruments in London, which I didn't.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the guy in London [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] was a personal friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when I told him who I'd worked for, he said, I know him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We have met on many a seminar, you see?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I got home, it came to my mind that this guy was going to write to Lou Davis.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I wrote an airmail letter to Lou Davis.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I said, I've applied for a job here, and I told him I'd worked for you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'd be very happy if you'd give me a good [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] letter, you see.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "A letter came to me that morning-- an airmail letter-- that was a copy, a carbon copy-- at that time, they weren't using Xerox.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a carbon copy of the letter he sent back that, if he engaged me, his gain would be his loss, you see?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And as I'm working in the store, I get a telephone call.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Listen to this story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I get a telephone call, can you come in to work tomorrow?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I said, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I told Henry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He says, go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But he said to me-- I said to him, how much should I ask for wages?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because I wasn't acquainted with the wage scale.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So he says, you ask for $100 a week, you see.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So it came out-- with the take-out pay in taxes-- I was getting $82.03, which you still could make a living at that time.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "How long did you work at--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wait a minute.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Wait a minute.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
